Package: PricingBandits
Type: Package
Title: Multi-Armed Bandit Approaches to Pricing Experiments
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Ian N. Weaver", "", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "i.weaver@nus.edu.sg"), 
               person("Vineet Kumar", "", role = "aut"), 
               person("Lalit Jain", "", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Ian N. Weaver <i.weaver@nus.edu.sg>
Description: Implements multiple multi-armed bandit approaches for pricing experiments, as discussed in the paper 'Nonparametric Pricing Bandits Leveraging Informational Externalities to Learn the Demand Curve' by Weaver, Kumar, and Jain.
